<template><div><h1 id="isextensible" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#isextensible"><span>isExtensible</span></a></h1>
<p><code v-pre>Object.isExtensible()</code> 方法用于检测指定对象是否可扩展。</p>
<h2 id="语法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#语法"><span>语法</span></a></h2>
<p>语法：</p>
<div class="language-js line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="js" data-title="js" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre v-pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#E5C07B">Object</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">isExtensible</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">(</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#E06C75">o</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">);</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A0A1A7;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#7F848E;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic">// o 指定用于检测的对象</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A0A1A7;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#7F848E;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic">// 返回 Boolean类型的值表示用于检测的对象是否可扩展</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="方法说明" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#方法说明"><span>方法说明</span></a></h2>
<p>默认情况下，对象是可扩展的：即可以为他们添加新的属性。</p>
<p><code v-pre>Object.preventExtensions</code>、<code v-pre>Object.seal</code> 或 <code v-pre>Object.freeze</code> 方法都可以标记一个对象为不可扩展（non-extensible）。</p>
